<br>
Cleric based rotation.  You are added to the rotation on the day and time that you receive your shimmering pearl.<br>
<br>
The top cleric on the list has 2 hours to clear the spawn.  <br>
<br>
If the spawn is not cleared, the top three clerics on the list are in FCFS competition for the mob.  <br>
<br>
If the mob is still not cleared after 6 hours, the first cleric on the list with a force strong enough to take the mob may take him down.<br>
<br>
The order of the list never changes.  People just drop off, or are added to the bottom.<br>
<br>
